      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773679618163,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "TIps :- \nif a class can belong to multiple classes \nthen most of the case it is not composition but \nit is aggregation\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TIps :- \nif a class can belong to multiple classes \nthen most of the case it is not composition but \nit is aggregation\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QvmLxFnM1qK41ndtccW57",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 125.04046526977208,
      "y": 1265.80052311818,
      "width": 721.4757080078125,
      "height": 360,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "cross-hatch",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2d",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 554664767,
      "version": 396,
      "versionNonce": 31651601,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773680246044,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "SOLID PRINCIPLES :- \n\n\n1. SRP - Single Resposibility Principle\n2. OCP - Open Closed Principle\n3. LSP - Liskov Substitute principle\n4. ISP - Interface Seggregation Principle\n5. DIP - Dependency Inversion Principle",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "SOLID PRINCIPLES :- \n\n\n1. SRP - Single Resposibility Principle\n2. OCP - Open Closed Principle\n3. LSP - Liskov Substitute principle\n4. ISP - Interface Seggregation Principle\n5. DIP - Dependency Inversion Principle",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
