      "updated": 1774613048726,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Mostly to fix this we use the \nStretegy Design Pattern",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Mostly to fix this we use the \nStretegy Design Pattern",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "CblQh3LmJzcjaPkTiD9hs",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 590.4618755933318,
      "y": 2817.7294305878463,
      "width": 874.639404296875,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3p",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 238372200,
      "version": 515,
      "versionNonce": 1171790872,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774613464684,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Which ever class needs to be extended \nsimple uska interface banao and for each \nmethods which we need to extend we need \nconcreate classes for them like \nIPaymentOperations : Pay() \nPayWithUPI implements IPaymentOperatiosn : Pay( implementation of upi payment)\nPayWithAmexCard implemts IPaymentOperations : Pay ( implementation of Amex payment )\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Which ever class needs to be extended \nsimple uska interface banao and for each \nmethods which we need to extend we need \nconcreate classes for them like \nIPaymentOperations : Pay() \nPayWithUPI implements IPaymentOperatiosn : Pay( implementation of upi payment)\nPayWithAmexCard implemts IPaymentOperations : Pay ( implementation of Amex payment )\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
