      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774789010078,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Bad way to fix it is simle client me loop me if else daldo or handle this edge case \nin client but this is bad code doing this we break OCP, also DRY, Also it is tightly coupled\nclient should be only know the Interface not the actuall diffrent type of its implementations\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
